[
  {
    "id": 469,
    "Name": "Gambler",
    "Card_Key": "gambler-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Gambler</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have learned that fortune favors the prepared — and the reckless.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When luck could plausibly tip your way,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Call It</strong> — name one small true thing about this <strong>Scene</strong>; the GM builds from it</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Ride the Wave</strong> — press your luck; take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next check where chance matters</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Tip the Table</strong> — nudge fate toward an ally; they take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on their next check</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 470,
    "Name": "Field Medic",
    "Card_Key": "field-medic-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Field Medic</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You know what to do when someone is bleeding and the clock is running.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When precision matters and the pressure is high,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Steady the Hand</strong> — your hands do exactly what they must; take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on the careful action</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Hold Them Together</strong> — keep someone beside you calm enough to do their part</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Work the Margin</strong> — narrate the small, exact thing that keeps it from getting worse</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 471,
    "Name": "Inspector",
    "Card_Key": "inspector-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Inspector</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You notice what others walk past — the detail that changes everything.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When close study could reveal what others missed,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Probe</strong> — ask the GM one honest question about what you're studying; they answer truthfully</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Spot the Tell</strong> — name one detail that doesn't fit; the GM confirms if it's there</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Name the Risk</strong> — name the fastest way this goes wrong; the GM answers honestly</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 472,
    "Name": "Trade Road Courier",
    "Card_Key": "trade-road-courier-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Trade Road Courier</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have carried messages and names across distances most people never cross.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When a familiar face or name could change how this moment goes,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Known Face</strong> — declare who or what recognizes you; the GM plays it accordingly</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Dropped Name</strong> — invoke a connection; one NPC shifts their stance</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Fast Talk</strong> — slip through on reputation; take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on your next social check</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 473,
    "Name": "Cutpurse",
    "Card_Key": "cutpurse-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Cutpurse</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">Your hands know routes that eyes never track.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When precision and control matter more than force,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Light Fingers</strong> — take or place something small, unseen</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Slip the Notice</strong> — move through a watched space as if you belong</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Misdirect</strong> — draw eyes elsewhere so the move lands clean</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 474,
    "Name": "Pit Fighter",
    "Card_Key": "pit-fighter-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pit Fighter</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have stood in places that would break most people and walked out standing.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When you deliberately face something that would shake anyone else,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Walk Into It</strong> — close the distance you're meant to flee; take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on what it takes</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Set the Tone</strong> — let them see you unbothered; steady an ally beside you</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Stare It Down</strong> — make the threatening thing hesitate</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 475,
    "Name": "Musician",
    "Card_Key": "musician-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Musician</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You feel the rhythm of a room before anyone else names it.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When timing is everything in this beat,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Right on the Beat</strong> — act at the exact moment it lands hardest</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Set the Pace</strong> — give the group a rhythm to move on together</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Feel the Turn</strong> — sense when the moment is about to change; call it</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 476,
    "Name": "Street-Raised",
    "Card_Key": "street-raised-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Street-Raised</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">The city taught you early that nothing stays still for long.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When things turn sharp or strange,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Already Knew</strong> — react as if you saw it coming — because part of you did</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Read the Angle</strong> — spot who benefits; say so</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Keep Your Footing</strong> — stay steady; give the others something to hold to</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 477,
    "Name": "Caravan Guard",
    "Card_Key": "caravan-guard-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Caravan Guard</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have learned to read people faster than you read terrain.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When differences would be a barrier between people,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Find Common Ground</strong> — name the thing both sides actually want</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Speak Their Way</strong> — frame it so it lands for them, not you</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Vouch</strong> — put your own standing behind someone to bridge the gap</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 478,
    "Name": "Pilgrim",
    "Card_Key": "pilgrim-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pilgrim</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You walk toward something larger than any single road.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When you meet someone driven by the same devotion,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Recognize the Road</strong> — name what you share; you both move easier for it</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Offer the Path</strong> — open a door only a fellow traveler would see</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Invoke It</strong> — call on the shared cause; one listener responds honestly</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 479,
    "Name": "Ascetic",
    "Card_Key": "ascetic-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Ascetic</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You have tested what you believe against pain, pressure, and doubt.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When your conviction is tested — by pain, pressure, or doubt,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Endure It</strong> — take the cost without bending; let it show</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Steady the Doubting</strong> — hold someone else's faith up when theirs slips</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Refuse the Bargain</strong> — turn down the easy way; narrate why</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  },
  {
    "id": 480,
    "Name": "Pathfinder",
    "Card_Key": "pathfinder-background",
    "HTML": "<div class=\"card bf-bg acc-background\"><div class=\"hdr\"><div class=\"hdr-top\"><span class=\"cap cap-accent\">Background</span></div><div class=\"hdr-name\">Pathfinder</div></div><div class=\"bf-body\"><div class=\"bf-flv\">You read uncertain ground the way others read faces.</div><div class=\"bf-react-gate\"><span class=\"cap cap-react-gate\">React</span><span class=\"bf-react-when\"> When you're navigating uncertain or dangerous ground,</span></div><div class=\"snap-intro\">Snap Check</div><div class=\"bf-choices\"><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Read the Land</strong> — name a feature of the terrain and how you'll use it</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Find the Way</strong> — pick the route others would miss; take <span class=\"kw kw-boost\">Boost 1</span> on the crossing</div><div class=\"bf-choice\"><strong>Set the Trail</strong> — lead so the group moves safe and quick</div></div><div class=\"snap-compact\"><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">1–3</span> Fails</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">4–8</span> Choose 1</span><span class=\"snap-dot\">·</span><span class=\"snap-chip\"><span class=\"kw kw-snap\">9+</span> Choose 2</span></div></div><div class=\"mill-float\" title=\"At scene start, you may discard this to draw 1.\"><span class=\"kw kw-mill\">Mill</span></div></div>",
    "Last_Rework_Date": "2026-06-30"
  }
]
